summary: Multiple fatalities and injuries have occurred in a tragic shooting at a grocery store in Fordyce, Arkansas. Three people were killed and 10 others were injured, including two officers. summary: The automotive world is abuzz with the announcement of Bugatti's latest masterpiece, the Tourbillon. This hybrid hypercar boasts an awe-inspiring 1,800 horsepower, making it a worthy successor to the legendary Chiron. With a price tag of $4.6 million, the Tourbillon is an exclusive marvel. Its striking design features a novel steering wheel that resembles a timepiece's tourbillon. The Tourbillon is scheduled for release in 2026, and while details are still emerging, it promises to be an automotive icon that will forever leave its mark on the industry.

summary: Lilly King, an Indiana native and Olympic swimmer, has qualified for the Paris Olympics in the 200-meter breaststroke. Her accomplishments at the trials were met with celebration, as she received a proposal and an engagement ring at the event. King expressed her joy at the proposal, calling it a "really special" moment.

name: NJ Transit
summary: New Jersey Transit and Amtrak commuters are facing more delays and cancellations this summer as repairs and upgrades are planned for the railways. Several recent incidents have caused disruptions, including a disabled Amtrak train and wire issues at New York Penn Station. Power issues have also suspended services, leaving commuters stranded and facing long waits. These ongoing disruptions come at a difficult time for commuters, who have already endured a challenging week with multiple suspensions and delays. Despite these setbacks, NJ Transit and Amtrak are working to restore services and minimize disruptions for the upcoming summer season.

name: Donald Sutherland
summary: Renowned actor Donald Sutherland, known for his captivating performances in films like "MASH," "Klute," and "The Hunger Games," has passed away at the age of 88. Sutherland was a versatile performer, excelling in portraying off-beat authority figures throughout his illustrious career that spanned over seven decades and included over 140 films and television shows. His diverse filmography showcased his ability to bring depth and complexity to a wide range of characters, leaving an indelible mark on the entertainment industry.

Caruso, known for his defensive prowess, has been a key contributor to the Bulls' success in recent seasons. Giddey, on the other hand, is a skilled playmaker with a bright future, making him a valuable addition to the Bulls' young core. The trade marks a significant change in strategy for the Thunder, who are reportedly looking to prioritize experience and defense.

name: Full moon
summary: In June 2024, the full moon, known as the "Strawberry Moon," will occur near the summer solstice, creating a unique celestial event. The moon's proximity to the solstice will result in a particularly bright and colorful appearance. The name "Strawberry Moon" originates from Native American traditions that associated the ripening of strawberries with the June full moon. This astronomical phenomenon is highly anticipated and is expected to provide a captivating celestial display.

name: Celtics parade
summary: Boston is celebrating the Boston Celtics' NBA championship victory with a victory parade. The parade will be held on Friday, June 21st, and is expected to draw over a million fans. The parade will start at 11am at the Boston Garden and will end at City Hall Plaza. There will be rolling road closures along the parade route, so it is important to plan ahead for traffic. The MBTA will be providing additional service for the parade, so fans are encouraged to take public transportation. The Celtics' victory is a major cause for celebration in Boston, as it is the team's first NBA championship since 2008 and their 18th NBA championship overall.
